Class FileClackData

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.ClackData
      • data.FileClackData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FileClackData
extends ClackData
    Subclass of ClackData that is used to deal with sending files. Can be of type CONSTANT_SENDFILE.
    Author:
    Matt Hansen
